# TaxBackwards.ca ŌĆö Design Rules

## Colour Tokens

All colours are defined as CSS custom properties. Never hardcode a hex value 
outside of `:root` / `[data-theme="light"]` definitions in `style.css`.

### Dark mode (default ŌĆö `:root`)
- `--page-bg: #162640`
- `--card-bg: #1e3352`
- `--accent: #3b82f6`
- `--accent-hover: #2563eb`
- `--success: #10b981`
- `--border: #2e4a6a`
- `--text-primary: #f1f5f9`
- `--text-secondary: #8eaabf`
- `--text-muted: #5d7d96`

### Light mode ŌĆö `[data-theme="light"]`
- `--page-bg: #e8edf5`
- `--card-bg: #ffffff`
- `--accent: #2563eb`
- `--accent-hover: #1d4ed8`
- `--success: #059669`
- `--border: #cbd5e1`
- `--text-primary: #0f172a`
- `--text-secondary: #475569`
- `--text-muted: #94a3b8`

Logo red `#CC2936` is hardcoded only inside SVG files. Never use it in CSS.

## Typography

- Font: Inter, loaded from Google Fonts with SRI hash
- Fallback: `-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, sans-serif`
- Brand title: 28px / 700 (22px on mobile)
- Section labels: 11px / 500 / uppercase / `letter-spacing: 0.08em`
- Input values: 18px / 600
- Output pre-tax value: 32px / 700 (24px on mobile)
- Output tax values: 24px / 700
- Body: 14px / 400
- Helper/disclaimer: 11px / 400
- Minimum font size: 11px ŌĆö never go below this

## Layout

- Single centred column, `max-width: 480px`
- Card: 32px padding, 16px border-radius, themed `box-shadow`
- Mobile (< 480px): full width, 20px padding
- Minimum 24px vertical gap between field groups
- Results section separated from inputs with a CSS `border-bottom` divider ŌĆö never `<hr>`
- All touch targets minimum 44px height

## Components

**Inputs**
- Padding: 14px top/bottom, 16px left/right
- Border-radius: 8px
- Focus ring: `0 0 0 3px rgba(37,99,235,0.15)`

**Calculate button**
- Full width, 48px height, 8px border-radius
- Hover: `translateY(-1px)`, `transition: all 0.15s ease`

**Copy buttons**
- Pill shape: `border-radius: 20px`
- Ghost style at rest; flash filled for 1.2s on click

**Auditor toggle**
- Custom CSS only ŌĆö no native checkbox
- Transition: `0.2s ease`
- `aria-checked` and `role="switch"` required

**Tooltips**
- CSS only ŌĆö no JavaScript
- Arrow pointer, appear above trigger

**Verified badge**
- Pill shape, faint green background, green border and text

**Province dropdown**
- Custom arrow, no default browser styling
- "Coming Soon" options: `disabled`, italic, muted colour

## Theme Switching

- `data-theme` attribute on `<html>` element; default value `"dark"`
- All colour transitions: `0.3s ease`
- `localStorage` key: `tb-theme`
- Respect `prefers-color-scheme` on first visit
- Inline script in `<head>` sets `data-theme` before first paint ŌĆö no flash of wrong theme

## Logo & Images

- `logo.svg` in an `<img>` tag in the header ŌĆö not inline SVG, not a CSS background
- `logo-print.svg` swapped only via `@media print`
- `favicon.svg` referenced in `<link rel="icon">` in `<head>`
- All images live in `public/images/`
- No raster images anywhere on the page

## Accessibility

- All inputs have visible `<label>` elements
- `aria-invalid` set on inputs with errors
- Error messages in `<span>` with `id` referenced by `aria-describedby`
- Focus ring never removed ŌĆö only restyled
- WCAG AA contrast minimum in both modes
- Toggle switches require `aria-checked` and `role="switch"`

## Print Styles (`@media print`)

- Hide: theme toggle, calculate button, copy buttons, auditor toggle
- Swap `logo.svg` ŌåÆ `logo-print.svg`
- Force white background, black text regardless of active theme
- Results section always visible

## Scrollbar

- Width: 6px
- Track: `var(--page-bg)`
- Thumb: `#334155`
- Thumb hover: `#475569`

## What Cursor Must Never Do

- Never use `innerHTML` ŌĆö always `textContent`
- Never hardcode a hex colour outside `:root` variable definitions
- Never use a framework or external CSS library (no Tailwind, Bootstrap, etc.)
- Never use `<hr>` for dividers
- Never remove focus rings
- Never use the word "refund" in any visible text
- Never place disclaimer text anywhere except directly below the calculate button
